snippet.textDisplay:
The evolution of this crazy, brilliant band is absolutely awe-inspiring. Thank you so much for continuing to make this art.

In my opinion, Gorillaz haven’t faltered for a second in their musical journey. Every new venture brings something fresh and inspiring to the table. Humanz was erratically rebellious, The Now Now was a melancholic dream, and Sound Machine sounds like one of their coolest projects to date. Phases 1 - 3 were iconic, but I truly LOVE this new era of Gorillaz. The passion has always been evident in Damon and Jamie’s work, and I can’t wait to see what else they have in store for us with Sound Machine!! 💕
